Previously crit damage would not take into account if you were using a bracer or not. It would however still factor in  up to 20% increase in damage from the 1005 AFTER the crit was factored in so basically:<br>
1005 x 2 + 201 damage (20% of 1005) = 2211 (previous high)<br>
<br>
Now it's calculating our crits after bracer damage<br>
(1005 x 1.2) x 2 = 2412<br>
<br>
